                <li>Real-time meme creation</li>
                <li>Second-screen experience with stats and commentary</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Modern Twists</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Virtual watch parties for distant friends</li>
                <li>Plant-based alternatives to traditional snacks</li>
                <li>Fantasy football final celebrations</li>
                <li>International viewing parties</li>
                <li>Sustainable party supplies</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ol>

